h \in \mathbb{N}
\left| \frac{1}{n} \sum_{m=1}^n e^{2 \pi i h (2 \pi m)} \right|?
\left| \frac{1}{n} \sum_{m=1}^n e^{2 \pi i h (2 \pi m)} \right| =\left| \frac{1}{n} \sum_{m=1}^n q^m \right|  =\left| \frac{q}{n} \frac{1-q^n}{1-q}\right| \le \frac{2}{n\left|1-q\right|}
q:=e^{(2 \pi)^2 i h}
